    "data": [
        {
            "title": "「賣出美國」交易再起 司法部發出傳票引發聯儲會獨立性擔憂",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><span class=\"news-dateline\">【彭博】--</span> 「賣出美國」情緒周一席捲市場，川普政府加大對<a class=\"link\" data-i13n=\"sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link\" data-ylk=\"slk:聯儲會;sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link;itc:0\" href=\"https://hk.finance.yahoo.com/tag/聯儲會\">聯儲會</a>的攻擊力度，加劇投資者對央行自主權的擔憂。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">美元、美債和美國股指期貨周一早盤全線下跌，此前聯儲會主席鮑威爾表示，司法部發出的刑事訴訟威脅，是政府和聯儲會在貨幣政策上的分歧所致。這一行動是針對聯儲會一系列施壓中的又一次，比如解雇理事庫克、屢次呼籲大幅降息等。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">市場跌勢引發了關於川普能在多大程度上影響利率立場的爭論，而貨幣政策立場長期以來都被視為在聯儲會的專責範圍內。這也再次引發了關於投資者是否應該減少美國資產和美元敞口的疑問，去年4月在川普宣布全面加徵關稅時，這一主題就曾主導全球市場。</p><div class=\"bg-toast-background -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0 lg:mx-auto lg:w-[300px] lg:pb-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-d3554721-176d-308c-9043-348284deb5d2-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">「任何引發人們對聯儲會獨立性質疑的事態發展都會增加美國貨幣政策的不確定性，」Allspring Global Investments的投資組合經理Gary Tan表示。「這可能會強化目前擺脫對美元依賴的多元化趨勢，並增加投資者對黃金等傳統對沖工具的興趣。」</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit\"><img alt=\" \" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"540\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/jZQX41t150ROnCu.obVkCA--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTU0MDtjZj13ZWJw/https://media.zenfs.com/no/bloomberg_chinese_traditional_757/c8bdc08a3ffe55a503e77a8c6366002d\" width=\"960\"/><figcaption class=\"text-px14 text-dolphin mt-2 wrap-anywhere\" style=\"max-width:960px\"> </figcaption></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">鮑威爾表示，大陪審團傳票與他6月在國會就聯儲會總部翻修工程的證詞有關，但應該「放在政府威脅和持續施壓的更廣泛背景下看待」。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">對投資者來說，局勢升級預示著市場波動性將加劇，因為這可能對長期貨幣政策產生影響。這也使美元成為關注焦點，美元在世界貿易中占據主導地位，占外匯交易額的近90%。歐洲央行管理委員會成員Francois Villeroy de Galhau上周警告稱，政府對聯儲會的批評正在威脅美元的地位。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">彭博策略师表示：</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">“鉴于鲍威尔在履行美联储主席职责方面有受到阻碍的风险，宏观交易员料将倾向于做空美元。”</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">MLIV时评策略师Mark Cranfield</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">彭博美元指數下跌0.2%，美元兌G-10貨幣幾乎全線走弱。標普500指數期貨下跌0.5%，那斯達克100指數期貨下跌0.8%。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">歐洲市場開盤後，美債走低，10年期殖利率漲近2個基點。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">原文標題Fed Subpoenas Revive ‘Sell America’ Trade on Autonomy Concerns</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">--聯合報導 Richard Henderson、Matthew Burgess.</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">More stories like this are available on <a class=\"link\" data-ylk=\"slk:bloomberg.com;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://www.bloomberg.com\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">bloomberg.com</a></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">©2026 Bloomberg L.P.</p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E8%B3%A3%E5%87%BA%E7%BE%8E%E5%9C%8B-%E4%BA%A4%E6%98%93%E5%86%8D%E8%B5%B7-%E5%8F%B8%E6%B3%95%E9%83%A8%E7%99%BC%E5%87%BA%E5%82%B3%E7%A5%A8%E5%BC%95%E7%99%BC%E8%81%AF%E5%84%B2%E6%9C%83%E7%8D%A8%E7%AB%8B%E6%80%A7%E6%93%94%E6%86%82-073337976.html",
            "pub_date": "2026-01-12 16:10:50",
