        {
            "title": "伊朗稱已平息抗議活動 並指控以色列和美國幕後煽動",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><span class=\"news-dateline\">【彭博】--</span> 伊朗外長表示，在持續兩周的動盪後，安全部隊已「完全掌控」國家局勢，並指責以色列和美國煽動全國性抗議活動，導致數百人喪生。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">伊朗外長阿拉格齊重申伊朗政府的指控，稱「暴亂分子和恐怖分子」使用「達伊沙式暴力」殺害警察和平民、破壞公共財產。此處「達伊沙」系伊斯蘭國的阿拉伯語縮寫。抗議活動持續至周一。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">阿拉格齊在接受國家電視台採訪時稱，「我們掌握大量證據，證明美國和以色列干涉了這場恐怖主義戰爭」，並補充道，「以色列直接負有責任，而美國通過煽動暴力的言論也難辭其咎。」</p><div class=\"bg-toast-background -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0 lg:mx-auto lg:w-[300px] lg:pb-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-29899908-61db-3f66-9814-b6f90fe7c7e0-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">推薦閱讀：[深度] 伊朗抗議浪潮愈演愈烈 一場可能改寫全球格局的革命悄然逼近</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">原文標題Iran Says It’s Quelled Protests After Hundreds Reported Killed</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">More stories like this are available on <a class=\"link\" data-ylk=\"slk:bloomberg.com;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://www.bloomberg.com\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">bloomberg.com</a></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">©2026 Bloomberg L.P.</p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E4%BC%8A%E6%9C%97%E7%A8%B1%E5%B7%B2%E5%B9%B3%E6%81%AF%E6%8A%97%E8%AD%B0%E6%B4%BB%E5%8B%95-%E4%B8%A6%E6%8C%87%E6%8E%A7%E4%BB%A5%E8%89%B2%E5%88%97%E5%92%8C%E7%BE%8E%E5%9C%8B%E5%B9%95%E5%BE%8C%E7%85%BD%E5%8B%95-104535450.html",
